ldapxx
------------------------------------------
C++ interface to ldap.h

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libldapxx-devel-0.1.5-1bl2
  libldapxx0-0.1.5-1bl2
  libopenldap2-2.6.10-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1
  openldap-devel-2.6.10-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/de-vri-es/ldapxx

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/de-vri-es/ldapxx/archive/refs/tags/0.1.5.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ldapxx-0.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ldapxx-0.1.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ldapxx-0.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ldapxx-0.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libldapxx0-0.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libldapxx-devel-0.1.5-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ldapxx)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ldapxx.README
  /usr/share/doc/ldapxx/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/ldapxx/README.md

(libldapxx0)
  /usr/bin/cygldapxx-0.dll

(libldapxx-devel)
  /usr/include/ldapxx/connection.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/detail/walk_result.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/error.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/options.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/types.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/util.hpp
  /usr/include/ldapxx/walk_result.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/ldapxx/ldapxxConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/ldapxx/ldapxxConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/ldapxx/ldapxxTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/ldapxx/ldapxxTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libldapxx.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ldapxx.pc

